{
  "stem": "15694.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And but he was tall and big with it-- obese.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said to-- let's start.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the young fellow was brought up, and he was-- his hands were tied behind his back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was near the front, and I heard him plead and say in German, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm innocent.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we knew that wouldn't-- I mean, anything wouldn't sort of help.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was suddenly this OD man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "OD stands for the German word of [GERMAN], order, serving in the name of the order.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I am not sure how to pro-- translate a German word.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They called OD men, the pol-- the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was Salz with the two stripes who had to hang the boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he had to do the job, and the pleading didn't help.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "No when he was hung up and a chair pus-- pushed away from underneath him, the rope broke.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And for a second or two, I thought, remember that by international law if something like that happened, it's like God's judgment, and the men will be freed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But as I say, a second or two only, but it wouldn't happen here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And a man on his tummy and with the hands tied crawled towards Goeth and repeated his pleas of course, and he pushed him away with his boot.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then I heard him say to the OD man, Salz, if it happens again, you hang.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now the OD man, of course, doubled the rope, and the boy was duly hanged and died.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I thought to myself, it may be a, a longer or more lingering death because it wasn't like cutting in like a rope, which sort of usually breaks your neck, but it was a double.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
